<span id="fn_1358"></span>[221:11](kj073.htm#fr_1362.md) *I.e.*, probably.
"prince land-pacifier." The first element of the compound is sometimes
omitted.

<span id="fn_1359"></span>[221:12](kj073.htm#fr_1363.md) *Wani no omi*.
